Text: and how exactly does one play a WEBM file?!?

ok let me answer my own question. right click on the downloaded webm file, 'play with firefox' or whatever browser you are using and it plays within that browser. kinda cool actually, sorry for my initial annoyance...
There are tons of players...just select an option Open with, than choose your fav.
